{"tid":2213848,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"驗樓師熱褲上鏡惹哄動　網民讚「四季戰衣」：好索呀！","createTime":"2020-09-23T00:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T00:33:03.000Z","uid":137088,"like":15,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2aca620844c63b5c265208fb7db794b975ef258c","tid":2213848,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:08:46.000Z","msg":"提起驗樓，不少人都會立即想到香港專業驗樓學會會長、資深驗樓師詹濟南（詹Sir）。近日詹Sir接受傳媒訪問，講及驗樓需用到的工具遭到禁運，擔心或因攜帶相關工具有被捕風險。報道引來關注，網民除了關心詹Sir的工作情況外，更被他上鏡時穿着的一身紅色Polo恤襯貼身熱褲驚艷，不禁留言大讚：「迷死人！」<br />\n<br />\n貴為「驗樓王」，詹Sir詹濟南不時接受各大傳媒邀請，驗收不同發展商的新盤單位，講述樓宇問題時不但專業詳盡，其幽默風格也深得不少網民支持。早前他就接受訪問，直言擔心攜帶「搵食工具」或會被誤當有不法用途而有被捕風險，更指現時已不敢攜帶雷射筆去驗樓，以免出現「秀才遇着兵，有理說不清」的尷尬情況。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民看過報道都關注詹Sir的工作情況，亦有人「錯重點」，將着眼點放於詹Sir出鏡時的一身打扮。相中可見，詹Sir穿着招牌紅色Polo恤，配上超短貼身熱褲，露出雙腿的造型非常吸睛，難怪有網民留言大讚，「你條熱褲好索呀！」、「全程控制唔到對眼望住佢條熱褲」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，詹Sir多年來一直以「紅Polo配長短牛仔褲」的招牌造型出鏡，資深觀眾一看報道即指「呢件紅Tee標記起碼廿年」，更有人形容為「四季戰衣」，可見詹Sir的形象深入民心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200921/384673034373566464.jpeg/wnhKsKdbtDdOXnrHWU8EDEHAGpN7Stjhoa9A06GvQNM?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200921%2F384673034373566464.jpeg%2FwnhKsKdbtDdOXnrHWU8EDEHAGpN7Stjhoa9A06GvQNM%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=e12b600a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"446eaaa75aa628a9cf1b06bca7a64326db29271c","tid":2213848,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"上身fit啲 冇左舊肥肉咪型<br />\n依家好撚柒"},{"pid":"82623dc66d80ac5ea77c5fda981b5842f6f39be3","tid":2213848,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:25:00.000Z","msg":"對腳幾光滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa342eff8a5d4aeeede53c85c3a96f41bca1e3b8","tid":2213848,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿叔又唔係操開就唔好露咁多啦"},{"pid":"f9b52e91370840908d567859329cee6c9a8faaf7","tid":2213848,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:30:03.000Z","msg":"條褲咩料🤔🤔🤔"},{"pid":"56f9119b115e7ac143a90c144498d9c4622429c9","tid":2213848,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:31:37.000Z","msg":"係咪有張女團制服圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69642c77e2e0830e45fdde74ad8d0a048357bf8e","tid":2213848,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fa342eff8a5d4aeeede53c85c3a96f41bca1e3b8","tid":2213848,"uid":98289,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿叔又唔係操開就唔好露咁多啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T00:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/j8Ovnk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fj8Ovnk.jpg&h=c8598932&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}